   &= 15 + 45 \\
   &= 60 \text{ spools}
   \end{align*}
   \]

3. **Find the Percentage of Blue Spools:**

   \[
   \begin{align*}
   \text{Percentage of Blue Spools} &= \left( \frac{\text{Blue Spools}}{\text{Total Spools}} \right) \times 100 \\
   &= \left( \frac{60}{150} \right) \times 100 \\
   &= 0.4 \times 100 \\
   &= 40\%
   \end{align*}
